OL,5, Links between Boris Johnson and BBC    
OL,6, chairman Richard Sharp are under fresh 
OL,7, scrutiny, following a report that the  
OL,8, then-prime minister was told to stop   
OL,9, asking Mr Sharp for financial advice.  
OL,11,FThe leaked memo, reported by the Sunday
OL,12,FTimes, was sent weeks before Mr Sharp  
OL,13,Fwas appointed to the corporation.      
OL,15,FMr Sharp has said he simply connected a
OL,16,Ffriend who wanted to guarantee a loan  
OL,17,Ffor Mr Johnson with the head of the    
OL,18,FCivil Service.                         
OL,20,FHe insists he was appointed on merit.  
